---
---
<section class="w-full bg-black grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 border-b-[6px] border-[var(--color-brand-primary)] overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Left Side: Clean, High-contrast text content on solid black (Elevated layer z-20) -->
  <div class="relative z-20 flex items-center bg-black py-16 px-8 sm:py-20 sm:px-16 lg:py-28 lg:pl-24 lg:pr-16">
    <div class="max-w-xl">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-[42px] text-white font-bold leading-tight mb-6 drop-shadow-xl">
        THE PREMIER CHOICE FOR<br/>LUXURY AUTO DETAILING
      </h2>
      
      <!-- Small blue separator line -->
      <div class="w-12 h-1 bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] mb-8 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(28,117,188,0.5)]"></div>

      <p class="font-sans text-gray-300 text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-loose mb-6">
        Central FLA. Auto Detail LLC is Central Florida's premier provider for mobile detailing services. With years of experience in the industry; our team is dedicated to providing clients with the utmost experience for you and your vehicle.
      </p>
      
      <p class="font-sans text-gray-300 text-sm md:text-[15px] leading-loose mb-10">
        Completely mobile, licensed, and insured, we also deliver professional car detailing services directly to your home or office for the ultimate convenience. Central FLA. Auto Detail is dedicated to top quality, trust, and outstanding results—ensuring complete satisfaction with each and every detail.
      </p>
      
      <a href="#" class="inline-block bg-[var(--color-brand-primary)] text-white font-sans font-bold text-xs tracking-widest py-4 px-8 rounded-sm hover:bg-blue-600 transition-colors uppercase">
        SCHEDULE YOUR SHINE
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Right Side: Nudged under the text column to create a 2px physical overlap, killing subpixel gaps -->
  <div class="w-full h-[320px] sm:h-[450px] lg:h-auto min-h-full relative overflow-hidden -mt-[2px] lg:mt-0 lg:-ml-[2px] z-10">
    <img src="/assets/images/about-car.png" alt="Luxury car detailing" class="w-full h-full object-cover object-center lg:absolute lg:inset-0 scale-[1.05]" />
    <!-- Smooth cinematic fade transitions: Vertical on mobile, Horizontal on desktop (Ultra-narrow seam blend for maximum car visibility) -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-black/50 to-transparent lg:bg-gradient-to-r lg:from-black lg:via-black/20 lg:via-[12%] lg:to-transparent lg:to-[30%] pointer-events-none z-10"></div>
  </div>
</section>
